name: feasibility_bounded
brief:
HiGHS QP bounded feasibility

Bounded feasibility subroutine for QP.
Handles box constraints during active set updates.

algorithms.name: Bounded QP Starting Point via Cholesky
algorithms.math:
For box-constrained QP: min ½x'Qx + c'x s.t. l ≤ x ≤ u.
      1. Solve Qx = -c via Cholesky: LL' = Q, then L⁻¹(-c), L'⁻¹(·).
      2. Project to bounds: x̃_i = max(l_i, min(u_i, x_i)).
      3. Collect active bounds for initial working set.
algorithms.complexity: O(n³) for Cholesky, O(n²) for solves, O(n) for projection.
